      <scopecontent id="aspace_b8d7b8174c2430bee465a403e04c54fd">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Correspondence, legal papers, deeds, estate inventories and pencil portraits relating to the Seward family of Killingworth and Guilford, Connecticut. Also figuring in the collection are the Buell, Pierson, Smith and Steevens families.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
